      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you before you consider this purchase. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple deep scratches, dents, and possibly rust or fading paint in several areas. The interior is similarly worn, with notable damage to upholstery, trim, and surfaces throughout the cabin. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it to reliable running condition \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs parts. We strongly recommend a full inspection by a trusted mechanic prior to purchase. What you see is what you get, and we'd rather you know the full picture now than be disappointed later.",
