    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make any decisions. The exterior shows its age \u2014 you'll notice several scratches, some paint fading in places, and a couple of small dents that are visible upon close inspection. The interior has seen regular use, with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the door panels, and general signs of everyday wear throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without its quirks \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a solid candidate for a buyer who is comfortable with a project vehicle or someone looking for reliable basic transportation at an accessible price point. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises.",
